<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: #DC2626; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .content { background: #f9fafb; padding: 30px; }
        .warning { background: #FEE2E2; border-left: 4px solid #DC2626; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .button { display: inline-block; background: #DC2626; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .footer { text-align: center; color: #6b7280; font-size: 12px; padding: 20px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Payment Failed - Urgent Action Required</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hi {{ user.email }},</p>
            
            <div class="warning">
                <strong>⚠️ Your subscription payment has failed.</strong>
            </div>
            
            <p>We've attempted to charge your payment method for {{ team.name }}'s {{ subscription.plan.name }} subscription, but the payment was unsuccessful.</p>
            
            <p><strong>Retry Status:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>Attempt: {{ retry_count }} of 3</li>
                <li>Retries remaining: {{ retries_remaining }}</li>
                {% if grace_period_ends_at %}
                <li>Grace period ends: {{ grace_period_ends_at|date('M d, Y') }}</li>
                {% endif %}
            </ul>
            
            {% if retries_remaining > 0 %}
            <p>We will automatically retry the payment, but we recommend updating your payment method now to avoid any service interruption.</p>
            {% else %}
            <p><strong>Final Notice:</strong> This is our last attempt. If payment fails again, your subscription will be suspended.</p>
            {% endif %}
            
            <a href="{{ url('payment_methods') }}" class="button">Update Payment Method</a>
            
            <p><strong>What happens if I don't update?</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>We'll retry the payment {{ retries_remaining }} more time{{ retries_remaining != 1 ? 's' : '' }}</li>
                <li>Your subscription will be suspended after all retries fail</li>
                <li>You'll lose access to {{ subscription.plan.name }} features</li>
            </ul>
            
            <p>Need help? Contact our support team immediately.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>© {{ 'now'|date('Y') }} SaaS Starter Pack. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
